The Saeki no Miyatsuko lineage is documented in the {{ill|Shinsen ShЕҚjiroku|ja|ж–°ж’°е§“ж°ҸйҢІ}}, appearing under the {{ill|Right Capital|ja|еҸідә¬}} Shinbetsu. They were originally known as "Saeki-be" and managed the Saeki-be labor group.

