The Saeki no Miyatsuko lineage is documented in the {{ill|Shinsen ShЕҚjiroku|ja|ж–°ж’°е§“ж°ҸйҢІ|1=Shinsen ShЕҚjiroku}}, appear[[Category:Important original categories]][[Category:japanese clans]]ing under the {{ill|Right Capital|ja|еҸідә¬}} Shinbetsu. They were originally known as "Saeki-be" and managed the Saeki-be labor group.
