The Saeki no Miyatsuko lineage is documented in the {{ill|Shinsen ShЕҚjiroku|ja|ж–°ж’°е§“ж°ҸйҢІ|1=Shinsen ShЕҚjiroku|qq=draft}}, appearing under the {{ill|Right Capital|ja|еҸідә¬|qq=draft}} Shinbetsu. They were originally known as "Saeki-be" and managed the Saeki-be labor group.

